    <title>LC1338</title>
    <url>/2021/07/06/LC1338/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h3 id="LeetCode-1338-Reduce-Array-Size-to-The-Half"><a href="#LeetCode-1338-Reduce-Array-Size-to-The-Half" class="headerlink" title="LeetCode 1338 Reduce Array Size to The Half"></a>LeetCode 1338 Reduce Array Size to The Half</h3><h4 id="题目描述"><a href="#题目描述" class="headerlink" title="题目描述"></a>题目描述</h4><p>题目链接：<a href="https://leetcode.com/problems/reduce-array-size-to-the-half/">https://leetcode.com/problems/reduce-array-size-to-the-half/</a></p>
<hr>
<p>Given an array arr.  You can choose a set of integers and remove all the occurrences of these integers in the array.</p>
<p>Return the minimum size of the set so that at least half of the integers of the array are removed.</p>
<p>题目给定一个数组 $A$，选择一个整数的集合 $S$，删除 $A$ 中所有 $S$ 中存在的元素，新集合 $A’$ 满足 $|A’| \leq |A|/2$，返回最小的集合 $S$.</p>
<hr>
<h4 id="解决方案"><a href="#解决方案" class="headerlink" title="解决方案"></a>解决方案</h4><h5 id="哈希-排序"><a href="#哈希-排序" class="headerlink" title="哈希 + 排序"></a>哈希 + 排序</h5><p>采用哈希+排序的思路，首先统计数组中各元素的频率，然后对这些频率进行排序，然后依次删除频率最高的元素，直至数组的元素个数小于或者等于原来的一半。</p>
<p>算法过程如下：</p>
<ol>
<li>创建哈希表，统计数组 $A$ 中各元素的频率；</li>
<li>将哈希表中的元素存放到新的数组中，并对数组进行排序；</li>
<li>若数组 $A$ 的长度为 $N$，则依次删除数组中频率最高的频率，从 $N$ 中进行扣除，直到数组中剩余的元素小于或者等于原来的一半。</li>
</ol>
<hr>
<h4 id="算法实现"><a href="#算法实现" class="headerlink" title="算法实现"></a>算法实现</h4><p>本题的 C++ 实现方案如下所示：</p>
<h2 id=""><a href="#" class="headerlink" title=""></a><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Solution</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">minSetSize</span><span class="params">(<span class="built_in">vector</span>&lt;<span class="keyword">int</span>&gt;&amp; arr)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">unordered_map</span>&lt;<span class="keyword">int</span>, <span class="keyword">int</span>&gt; countMap;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="keyword">int</span>&amp; num : arr) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            ++countMap[num];</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> N = <span class="keyword">static_cast</span>&lt;<span class="keyword">int</span>&gt;(arr.size());</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="keyword">int</span> bound = N &gt;&gt; <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">vector</span>&lt;<span class="keyword">int</span>&gt; freqs;</span><br><span class="line">        freqs.reserve(N);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="keyword">auto</span>&amp; kv : countMap) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            freqs.push_back(kv.second);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        sort(begin(freqs), end(freqs), [](<span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="keyword">auto</span>&amp; lhs, <span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="keyword">auto</span>&amp; rhs) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> lhs &gt; rhs;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> res = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="keyword">int</span>&amp; freq : freqs) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            N = N - freq;</span><br><span class="line">            ++res;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (N &lt;= bound) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> res;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></h2><h4 id="算法分析"><a href="#算法分析" class="headerlink" title="算法分析"></a>算法分析</h4><h5 id="时间复杂度"><a href="#时间复杂度" class="headerlink" title="时间复杂度"></a>时间复杂度</h5><p>假设数组 $A$ 的长度为 $n$.</p>
<ol>
<li>统计 $A$ 中元素的频率，需要遍历一遍原来的数组，时间复杂度为 $\Theta(n)$.</li>
<li>存放哈希表中的频率值到新的数组中，时间复杂度为 $O(n)$.</li>
<li>排序的时间复杂度为 $O(n\lg n)$.</li>
<li>获取最终结果的时间复杂度为 $O(n)$.</li>
</ol>
<p>综合，算法的时间复杂度为 $O(n \lg n)$.</p>
<h5 id="空间复杂度"><a href="#空间复杂度" class="headerlink" title="空间复杂度"></a>空间复杂度</h5><p>额外的空间主要用到了哈希表和存放频率的数组，空间复杂度为 $O(n)$.</p>
]]></content>
