    <title>LC378</title>
    <url>/2021/07/07/LC378/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h3 id="LeetCode-378-Kth-Smallest-Element-in-a-Sorted-Matrix"><a href="#LeetCode-378-Kth-Smallest-Element-in-a-Sorted-Matrix" class="headerlink" title="LeetCode 378 Kth Smallest Element in a Sorted Matrix"></a>LeetCode 378 Kth Smallest Element in a Sorted Matrix</h3><h4 id="题目描述"><a href="#题目描述" class="headerlink" title="题目描述"></a>题目描述</h4><hr>
<p>题目链接：<a href="https://leetcode.com/problems/kth-smallest-element-in-a-sorted-matrix/">https://leetcode.com/problems/kth-smallest-element-in-a-sorted-matrix/</a></p>
<p>Given an <code>n x n</code> <code>matrix</code> where each of the rows and columns are sorted in ascending order, return <em>the</em> <code>kth</code> <em>smallest element in the matrix</em>.</p>
<p>Note that it is the <code>kth</code> smallest element <strong>in the sorted order</strong>, not the <code>kth</code> <strong>distinct</strong> element.</p>
<p><strong>Example 1:</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Input: matrix &#x3D; [[1,5,9],[10,11,13],[12,13,15]], k &#x3D; 8</span><br><span class="line">Output: 13</span><br><span class="line">Explanation: The elements in the matrix are [1,5,9,10,11,12,13,13,15], and the 8th smallest number is 13</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>Constraints:</p>
<ul>
<li>n == matrix.length</li>
<li>n == matrix[i].length</li>
<li>1 &lt;= n &lt;= 300</li>
<li>-109 &lt;= matrix[i][j] &lt;= 109</li>
<li>All the rows and columns of matrix are guaranteed to be sorted in non-decreasing order.</li>
<li>1 &lt;= k &lt;= n2</li>
</ul>
<p>题目需求是求出二维数组中第 $k$ 小的数，并且二维数组满足每一行和每一列都是单调递增的。</p>
<hr>
<h4 id="解决方案"><a href="#解决方案" class="headerlink" title="解决方案"></a>解决方案</h4><h5 id="Heap"><a href="#Heap" class="headerlink" title="Heap"></a>Heap</h5><p>使用最小堆实现的优先队列 $Q$ 来解决本问题，有点像类似解决合并 $k$ 个有序链表的算法，我们的算法步骤如下所示：</p>
<ol>
<li>将矩阵 $M$ 中每一行的第一个元素加入到 $Q$.</li>
<li>取出 $Q$ 中的顶部元素，并将相应行的下一个元素加入到 $Q$.</li>
<li>步骤 2 重复 $k-1$ 次。</li>
</ol>
<hr>
<h4 id="算法实现"><a href="#算法实现" class="headerlink" title="算法实现"></a>算法实现</h4><h5 id="Heap-1"><a href="#Heap-1" class="headerlink" title="Heap"></a>Heap</h5><h6 id="C-实现结构和类的优先队列"><a href="#C-实现结构和类的优先队列" class="headerlink" title="C++ 实现结构和类的优先队列"></a>C++ 实现结构和类的优先队列</h6><p><a href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/16111337/declaring-a-priority-queue-in-c-with-a-custom-comparator/48587737">https://stackoverflow.com/questions/16111337/declaring-a-priority-queue-in-c-with-a-custom-comparator/48587737</a></p>
<p>需要定义一个类，并且重载 <code>operator()</code> 方法。</p>
<p>如果需要定义一个最小堆，可以写成如下的代码：</p>
<figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">Compare</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">bool</span> <span class="title">operator</span><span class="params">()</span> <span class="params">(<span class="keyword">const</span> T&amp; t1, <span class="keyword">const</span> T&amp; t2)</span> </span>&#123; <span class="comment">// T 为具体的类型</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> t1 &gt; t2; <span class="comment">// 假设已重载相应的比较方法 相应的定义最大堆应该写成 t1 &lt; t2.</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// priority_queue&lt;T, vector&lt;T&gt;, Compare&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h6 id="C-的代码实现如下所示："><a href="#C-的代码实现如下所示：" class="headerlink" title="C++ 的代码实现如下所示："></a>C++ 的代码实现如下所示：</h6><h2 id=""><a href="#" class="headerlink" title=""></a><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">Compare</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">bool</span> <span class="title">operator</span><span class="params">()</span> <span class="params">(tuple&lt;<span class="keyword">int</span>, <span class="keyword">int</span>, <span class="keyword">int</span>&gt;&amp; t1, tuple&lt;<span class="keyword">int</span>, <span class="keyword">int</span>, <span class="keyword">int</span>&gt;&amp; t2)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> get&lt;<span class="number">0</span>&gt;(t1) &gt; get&lt;<span class="number">0</span>&gt;(t2);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Solution</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">kthSmallest</span><span class="params">(<span class="built_in">vector</span>&lt;<span class="built_in">vector</span>&lt;<span class="keyword">int</span>&gt;&gt;&amp; matrix, <span class="keyword">int</span> k)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="keyword">int</span> rows = matrix.size();</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="keyword">int</span> cols = matrix[<span class="number">0</span>].size();</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">priority_queue</span>&lt;tuple&lt;<span class="keyword">int</span>, <span class="keyword">int</span>, <span class="keyword">int</span>&gt;, <span class="built_in">vector</span>&lt;tuple&lt;<span class="keyword">int</span>, <span class="keyword">int</span>, <span class="keyword">int</span>&gt;&gt;, Compare&gt; pq;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">int</span> r = <span class="number">0</span>; r &lt; rows; ++r) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            pq.push(make_tuple(matrix[r][<span class="number">0</span>], r, <span class="number">0</span>));</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">int</span> i = <span class="number">1</span>; i &lt; k; ++i) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            tuple&lt;<span class="keyword">int</span>, <span class="keyword">int</span>, <span class="keyword">int</span>&gt; node = pq.top();</span><br><span class="line">            pq.pop();</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="keyword">int</span> r = get&lt;<span class="number">1</span>&gt;(node);</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="keyword">int</span> c = get&lt;<span class="number">2</span>&gt;(node);</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (c &lt; cols<span class="number">-1</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                pq.push(make_tuple(matrix[r][c+<span class="number">1</span>], r, c+<span class="number">1</span>));</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> get&lt;<span class="number">0</span>&gt;(pq.top());</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></h2><h5 id="Binary-Search"><a href="#Binary-Search" class="headerlink" title="Binary-Search"></a>Binary-Search</h5><p>在本题中，二分查找采用范围查询，已知矩阵 $A$ 的最大值为 $A_{min}$，最大值为 $A_{max}$.</p>
<ul>
<li>使用二分查找，找出 $A^{x}$，使得 $A$ 中小于或者等于 $A^x$ 的元素的数目为 $k$.</li>
<li>直至找到最小的 $A^x$.</li>
</ul>
<p>下面我们证明 $A^*$ 在 $A$ 中必然存在：</p>
<ul>
<li>如果 $A’ = (A_{min}+A_{max})/2$，且 #$(A_i \leq A’) &gt; k$，则说明仍然存在 $A^x &lt; A’$，使得 #$(A_i \leq A^x) = k$，此时只需要缩小 $A_{max}$ 的范围即可；</li>
<li>如果 $A’ = (A_{min}+A_{max})/2$，且 #$(A_i \leq A’) &lt; k$，则说明仍然存在 $A^x &gt; A’$，使得 #$(A_i \leq A^x) = k$，此时只需要增大 $A_{min}$ 的范围即可；</li>
<li>如果 $A’ = (A_{min}+A_{max})/2$，且 #$(A_i \leq A’) = k$，此时 $[A^x,A’]$ 间的值都可以满足 #$(A_i \leq A^x) = k$，我们只需要缩小 $A_{max}$ 就可以找到 $A$ 中存在的值。</li>
</ul>
<p>C++ 代码如下所示：</p>
<h2 id="-1"><a href="#-1" class="headerlink" title=""></a><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Solution</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">kthSmallest</span><span class="params">(<span class="built_in">vector</span>&lt;<span class="built_in">vector</span>&lt;<span class="keyword">int</span>&gt;&gt;&amp; matrix, <span class="keyword">int</span> k)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="keyword">int</span> n = matrix.size();</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> lo = matrix[<span class="number">0</span>][<span class="number">0</span>], hi = matrix[n<span class="number">-1</span>][n<span class="number">-1</span>] + <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span> (lo &lt; hi) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">int</span> mid = lo + ((hi - lo) &gt;&gt; <span class="number">1</span>);</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">int</span> count = getCountSmallerEqual(matrix, mid);</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (count &lt; k) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                lo = mid + <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                hi = mid;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> lo;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">private</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">getCountSmallerEqual</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="built_in">vector</span>&lt;<span class="built_in">vector</span>&lt;<span class="keyword">int</span>&gt;&gt;&amp; matrix, <span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="keyword">int</span>&amp; val)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> n = matrix.size();</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> count = <span class="number">0</span>, c = n<span class="number">-1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">int</span> r = <span class="number">0</span>; r &lt; n; ++r) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">while</span> (c &gt;= <span class="number">0</span> &amp;&amp; matrix[r][c] &gt; val) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                --c;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            count += (c + <span class="number">1</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> count;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></h2><h4 id="算法分析"><a href="#算法分析" class="headerlink" title="算法分析"></a>算法分析</h4><h5 id="Heap-2"><a href="#Heap-2" class="headerlink" title="Heap"></a>Heap</h5><h6 id="时间复杂度"><a href="#时间复杂度" class="headerlink" title="时间复杂度"></a>时间复杂度</h6><ul>
<li>C++ 代码中的 13-15 行遍历 $A$ 的行，时间复杂度 $O(n)$.</li>
<li>C++ 代码中的 17-25 重复 $k-1$ 次获取最小元素的操作，每次操作均需要维护一个大小为 $n$ 的最小堆，时间复杂度为 $O(k \lg n)$.</li>
</ul>
<p>综合总的时间复杂度为 $O(n+k \lg n)$.</p>
<p>考虑到 $k$ 的取值范围 $[1, n^2]$，时间复杂度也可以是 $O(n^2 \lg n)$.</p>
<p>若 $k &lt; n$，则时间复杂度为 $O(n \lg n)$.</p>
<h6 id="空间复杂度"><a href="#空间复杂度" class="headerlink" title="空间复杂度"></a>空间复杂度</h6><p>使用堆的算法需要维护一个大小为 $n$ 的最小堆，空间复杂度为 $O(n)$.</p>
<h5 id="Binary-Search-1"><a href="#Binary-Search-1" class="headerlink" title="Binary-Search"></a>Binary-Search</h5><h6 id="时间复杂度-1"><a href="#时间复杂度-1" class="headerlink" title="时间复杂度"></a>时间复杂度</h6><ul>
<li>二分查找的时间复杂度为 $O(\lg (A_{max}-A_{min}))$.</li>
<li>内部嵌套的寻找小于或者等于算法的时间复杂度为 $O(n)$.</li>
</ul>
<p>因此，时间复杂度为 $O(n\lg (A_{max}-A_{min}))$.</p>
<h6 id="空间复杂度-1"><a href="#空间复杂度-1" class="headerlink" title="空间复杂度"></a>空间复杂度</h6><p>此算法不需要额外的空间，因此空间复杂度为 $O(1)$.</p>
]]></content>
